metadata.name: BLUE LADY WITH THE SCARF
metadata.description:
Original Hyperrealistic Ballpoint Drawing, drawn over 100 hours. this drawing was inspired by the dilemma and chaos the WORLD went through in the year 2020! 

I wanted to create this piece during that year but felt now was the right time to do this so we could reflect on the past and see how strong and sedulous wehave all become despite the chaos, riots, pains, and suffering.
